QuestData.Title: Holed Up
QuestData.Description: Oh thank you, thank you, thank you. If you hadn't come along...$B$BWait! There must be other survivors in the Nook like me!$B$BPlease, $c, I beg you. Rescue the rest of my citizens and deliver us safely to Shado-Pan Fallback.
QuestData.LogDescription: Rescue Jin Warmkeg, Ya Firebough, Old Lady Fung, and Sya Zhong.
